<section class="pg-section" data-section="Why Our Acne Facial Works When Other Treatments Haven't">
  <h2 class="pg-h">Why Our Acne Facial Works When Other Treatments Haven't</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Medical-grade ingredients that target acne at the source without damaging your skin barrier.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Targets Root Causes, Not Just Symptoms</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Our Acne Facial uses medical-grade actives like Salicylic Acid and Tea Tree to penetrate deep into pores, control oil at the source, and prevent future breakouts.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Balances Oil Without Stripping Your Skin</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Say goodbye to that tight, uncomfortable feeling. Our treatment controls excess sebum naturally, so your skin stays balanced and breakout-free without the dryness.</p>
