  <p class="pg-text">Centella Asiatica and Houttuynia Cordata calm redness, soothe irritation, and speed healing of active breakouts—without harsh chemicals or over-drying your skin.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Safe &amp; Gentle for All Skin Types</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Unlike harsh chemical peels or abrasive treatments, our acne facial is suitable for sensitive skin. No irritation, no downtime—just clearer, healthier skin after every visit.</p>
