<section class="pg-section" data-section="What To Expect During Your 70-Minute Acne Facial Experience">
  <h2 class="pg-h">What To Expect During Your 70-Minute Acne Facial Experience</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Every step is designed for your comfort and results. Here's exactly what happens during your 70-minute treatment at our Millburn spa.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Consultation &amp; Skin Analysis (5-10 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">We start with a thorough consultation to understand your skin concerns and acne triggers. Our expert esthetician analyzes your skin type and creates a customized treatment plan just for you.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Deep Cleansing &amp; Preparation (10-15 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Your skin is gently cleansed using the Corthe Dermo Cleansing Foam to remove makeup, oils, and impurities. This prepares your pores for deep treatment and ensures maximum product absorption.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Tea Tree Ampoule Treatment (10-15 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">We apply the Corthe Dermo Pure Tea Tree Ampoule, infused with 50% pure tea tree water. This powerful formula penetrates deep into pores to control oil production and fight acne-causing bacteria.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Purifying Mask Application (20-25 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">The Corthe Dermo Pure Purifying Mask is applied to absorb excess oil, reduce inflammation, and accelerate healing. You'll relax while the mask works to calm your skin and clear your pores.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Toner &amp; Moisturizer Application (5-10 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">We finish with the First Aid Toner and First Aid Lotion to balance your skin, lock in hydration, and protect against future breakouts. Your skin will feel refreshed, calm, and balanced.</p>
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/acne-facial">Schedule Now</a>
</section>

